President of the Senate, Abubakar Bukola Saraki, has visited Daura, Katsina State, to condole with the Emir Umar Farouk Umar, on the death of Senator Mustapha Bukar. Bukar who was 63 when he died on Wednesday was the Madawakin Daura. He represented Katsina north in the Senate, with President Muhammadu Buhari, among his constituents.